ontrols and backup protocols.  \n\n**Key Actions:**  \n1. Implement **RBAC and MFA** for sensitive data access.  \n   * **Informatica Solution:** **Cloud Data Access Management (CDAM)** for authentication logging.  \n2. Automate encrypted backups and test disaster recovery plans.  \n   * **Informatica Solution:** **Cloud Data Ingestion and Replication (CDIR)** for resilient backups.  \n\n---\n\n### 4. Data Retention & Erasure (25% Compliance)  \n**Risk Level:** High  \n**Implications:** Non-compliance with DPDP Section 8 erasure requirements.  \n\n**Key Actions:**  \n1. Automate policy-driven data deletion workflows.  \n   * **Informatica Solution:** Cloud-based erasure tools with **48-hour customer notifications**.  \n2. Align retention policies with DPDP Section 6(1)(e).  \n\n---\n\n### 5. Cross-Border Data Transfers (16.7% Compliance)  \n**Risk Level:** Critical  \n**Implications:** Regulatory action for violating data localization rules.  \n\n**Key Actions:**  \n1. Restrict transfers of specified data outside India.  \n   * **Informatica Solution:** **Cloud Data Integration** with region-specific processing.  \n\n---\n\n### 6. Children’s Data Protection (33.3% Compliance)  \n**Risk Level:** High  \n**Implications:** Penalties for lacking parental consent mechanisms.  \n\n**Key Actions:**  \n1. Implement **verifiable parental consent** and age-gating.  \n\n---\n\n## Prioritized Action Plan  \n1. **Immediate (0–30 days):**  \n   - Deploy **Informatica Data Subject Rights Management** for request handling.  \n   - Initiate data localization adjustments using **Cloud Data Integration**.  \n\n2. **Short-Term (30–90 days):**  \n   - Roll out **RBAC/MFA** via **CDAM**.  \n   - Automate erasure workflows with **Cloud Data Quality**.  \n\n3. **Ongoing:**  \n   - Quarterly audits using **Informatica Cloud Data Governance**.  \n\n---\n\n## Strategic Recommendations  \n* **Leverage Informatica’s end-to-end suite** to unify compliance efforts:  \n  - **Data Privacy Management** for classification.  \n  - **CDAM/CDIR** for security and backups.  \n  - **Log Analyzer** for audit trails.  \n\n**Partner with Informatica experts** to close gaps efficiently.  \n**Contact:** info@datainfa.com for DPDP implementation support.  \n```",
