edicated team to manage requests within regulatory deadlines.  \n\n---\n\n### 3. Data Security Measures (40.0%)  \n**Risk Level:** High  \n**Implications:** Weak access controls and monitoring increase breach risks.  \n\n**Action Items:**  \n1. Strengthen authentication with **Informatica Cloud Data Access Management (CDAM)**.  \n2. Enhance monitoring via **Informatica’s partnership with securiti.ai** for API threat detection.  \n\n---\n\n### 4. Data Breach Notification (0.0%)  \n**Risk Level:** Critical  \n**Implications:** Failure to report breaches within 72 hours may result in severe penalties.  \n\n**Action Items:**  \n1. Establish an automated breach detection and reporting protocol.  \n\n---\n\n### 5. Data Retention and Erasure (50.0%)  \n**Risk Level:** Medium  \n**Implications:** Manual processes delay compliance with erasure requests.  \n\n**Action Items:**  \n1. Automate erasure workflows using **Informatica data management solutions**.  \n\n---\n\n### 6. Children’s Data Protection (16.7%)  \n**Risk Level:** High  \n**Implications:** Lack of parental consent verification violates DPDP Section 10.  \n\n**Action Items:**  \n1. Integrate digital ID verification for parental consent.  \n2. Develop technical frameworks for age verification.  \n\n---\n\n### 7. Third-Party Processing (0.0%)  \n**Risk Level:** Critical  \n**Implications:** Unregulated third-party access risks data misuse.  \n\n**Action Items:**  \n1. Draft contracts mandating DPDP Section 6(f) compliance.  \n\n---\n\n### 8. Cross-Border Data Transfers (16.7%)  \n**Risk Level:** High  \n**Implications:** Unauthorized transfers violate localization norms.  \n\n**Action Items:**  \n1. Use **Informatica Cloud Data Integration** for region-specific processing.  \n2. Block unauthorized transfers through policy enforcement.  \n\n---\n\n## Prioritized Action Plan  \n1. **Immediate (0–3 months):**  \n   - Deploy **Informatica CDAM** for access controls.  \n   - Automate breach reporting and erasure processes.  \n2. **Medium-Term (3–6 months):**  \n   - Implement **Data Subject Rights Management**.  \n   - Finalize third-party contracts.  \n3. **Long-Term (6–12 months):**  \n   - Expand training and DPO appointment.  \n\n---\n\n## Strategic Recommendations  \n* **Leverage Informatica Solutions:**  \n  - **Cloud Data Governance** for documentation and auditability.  \n  - **Data Privacy Management** for sensitive data oversight.  \n* **Partner with Informatica Experts:** Close gaps efficiently with tailored support.  \n\n**Contact:** info@datainfa.com for DPDP implementation guidance.  \n```",
